Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday on you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天真是你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday, it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也是我创造你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the day that I built you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我过的最棒的一次生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This has been the best birthday I've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it ain't over yet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.65,0:01:34.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来让寿星拆礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:34.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for the birthday girl to open her presents
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是探戈课的礼品券
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a gift certificate for tango lessons
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我是很愿意与你共舞  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know I'd love to dance with you, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们以前试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we've tried this before
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you recall--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳得都不怎么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It did not go well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一次就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time is going to be different
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为另外一样生日礼物就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because your other birthday present is this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级无敌拉腿机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Leg Yanker Five Zillion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是为了你  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is for you, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice weather up here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  绿色邪恶高个儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hello, tall, green, and evil
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能与你共舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I have this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,548)}裤头村活动中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1356,430)}苏西格鲁夫舞蹈学校\N晚上七点半
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好爱你的长腿新模样  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love the new stems, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经晚上八点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's 8:00 p.m. already
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舞蹈老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's our dance instructor?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, class
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们的舞蹈老师  苏西格鲁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your tango instructor, Susie Groove
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我教完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And when I'm done with you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的舞步就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is how you gotta move
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家开始跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So everyone start dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会来给大家指导几下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll come around and give you some tips
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你第一条规矩就违反了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're breaking the first rule, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个探戈两人跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It takes two to tango
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.88,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 一个巴掌拍不响 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  格鲁夫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miss Groove
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs ordered me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚来当珍珍的探戈舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be Pearl's tango partner tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但她好像不太喜欢我的猛烈舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but she just doesn't dig my tangy moves
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你不会跳探戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you can't tango
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的可是真正的舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a real dance partner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是精力过剩  腿还打结的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not a cackling, bow-legged goofball
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No offense
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就当你是在夸我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took it as a compliment
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以教会大家跳探戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can teach anyone to tango
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会跳探戈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can tango
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多亏有苏西格鲁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Susie Groove
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳探戈不可以靠太近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's too close to tango
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松点  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Relax, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了  跳舞小能手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, my little whirling dervish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我这双腿不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but these legs have minds of their own
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱来  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that way, you idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Damn you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,镇静一点  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Compose yourself, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是公共场合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're in public
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是需要有个东西来帮我平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need something to balance me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Susie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚洗过腿  结果腿不听使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just washed my legs, and I can't do a thing with them
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题不在于腿  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Legs ain't your problem, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是想跳探戈  就要学会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to tango, you got to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用臀部去跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to dance with your hips
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用唇部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With my lips?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't working
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我说的是臀部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because I said hips
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you got to do is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你臀部还挺不俗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your hips are so hip
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你有得辛苦了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your work cut out for you, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的臀部又做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hips can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然做得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course they can
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须迫使臀部跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to force them to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳探戈要身心皆备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tango is physical, emotional
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且最重要的是  要霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and most importantly, aggressive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aggressive?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么一说我就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking my language
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我们可会霸道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we speak fluent aggression
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就多多利用霸道  施加在臀部上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tap into that aggression and put it in your hips
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, abrazo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Embrace
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abrazo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳得真不错  痞老板夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terrific tangoing, Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来以为我们跳得好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought we were good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这一说可真好心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How nice of you to say
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧紧相拥吧  我的臭奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abrazo, my stinky cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧紧相拥吧  我的烂玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abrazo, my rotten rose
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  我一不小心把钉条弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I accidentally dropped my spike strip
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oopsie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就是探戈王与探戈后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the king and queen of tango
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板夫妇  休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Planktons, take four
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板跟凯伦刚刚有点坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't very nice of Plankton and Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实挺坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但那就是探戈  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that's the tango, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳得好  痞老板夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bravo, Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霸道得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice aggression
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打磁盘碎片整理以来就没这么开心过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't had this much fun since I got defragged
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们就是全班第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say we're the best in the class
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说呢  格鲁夫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you, Miss Groove?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你们两个都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're both great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我的尖子生也许会不同意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my top students might disagree
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尖子生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top students?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们今天迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're late today
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探戈大师到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tango masters have arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王得换条干净内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass needed clean underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王和他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass and his mom?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟老妈已经赢了海底探戈锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother and I have won the Undersea Tango Championship
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连续三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three years in a row
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the best
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是不知怎的  毫无预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But yet somehow, and without warning
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才最强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're the best
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斗舞的气息扑面而来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell a dance-off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昆虫优先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Insects first
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来跳赢我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, try and out-tango that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们就跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if we do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说我们最强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said we're the best
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abrazo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有谁点了霸王三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone ordered a Bass sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was fun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们似乎还不够霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I guess we're not aggressive enough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,称不上最强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be the best
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不可能比我们还霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody is more aggressive than us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就只是练得多而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They just have more practice
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能有办法作弊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only there was some way we could cheat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们见识一下谁最强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and show them who's really the best
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是回去吧  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  这个从你口袋里掉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, this fell out of your pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的瑞瑞射线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my Ray-Ray ray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把我变成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the device that turns me into
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发型更帅的另一个人格  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my alter ego with great hair, Ray-Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以更霸道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll make me more aggressive
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我的瑞瑞可以掌控全局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Ray-Ray is the only one who could take charge of this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.73,0:09:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下瑞瑞  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Ray-Ray, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  射错老头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, wrong old man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下瑞瑞  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Ray-Ray, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有谁点了份冰冷的复仇大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone ordered a cold plate of revenge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要把脸丢光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With extra humiliation
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探戈重赛  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tango rematch, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Ray-Ray, go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我想恨痞老板夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to hate the Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他们也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,, but they're so good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跳舞的样子好像天使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He dances like an angel
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死亡天使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of death
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以探戈赋予我的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the tango vested in me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正式宣布凯伦与瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I pronounce Karen and Ray-Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的尖子生  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my top students, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Ray-Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the best
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  凯伦小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Karen-cakes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界之巅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,top of the world
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for the big finish
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摩擦力太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too much friction
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that's my line
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以借用我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can borrow my legs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的已经长回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine are growing back already
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个探戈两人跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It takes two to tango
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, Ray-Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下瑞瑞  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The name's Ray-Ray, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.35,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}食灵之书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1306,880)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,556)}咖啡壶
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐钱花得再多也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't mind overpaying if it's breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这钱看得我垂涎三尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That money looks tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能别闹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多吃早餐的  看得我又饿又渴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these people eating breakfast is making me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,渴望多来一点客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry for more customers that is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.10,0:12:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说到客人  别来烦我客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of customers, stop bothering mine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一踢开启了我的全新一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that sure kick-started my day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个金点子要用在蟹堡王上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a fantastic idea for me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去月球开蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're opening a Krusty Krab on the moon?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要永远关门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're closing down forever?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  蟹堡王要开始供应早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will start serving breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个要更早来上班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you two get to come to work even earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  我可以做蟹黄堡当早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I get to make Krabby Patties for breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家才不会一大早来吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People don't want patties in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家会想吃培根煎蛋和薯饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They want bacon and eggs and hash browns
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那种一般的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, breakfast stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你能不能当场做一份煎饼  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See if you can whip up a stack of pancakes, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃一口看看质量如何  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it the old mouth test, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这煎饼味道像蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These pancakes taste like a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我只会做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I only know how to cook Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就怕这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去一趟书店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go down to the bookstore
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我预订的早餐菜谱取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and pick up the breakfast cookbook I ordered
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得让你的本领稍微增进一点点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to expand your repertoire a bit, boy-o
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,512)}书
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  我来帮蟹老板取食谱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm here to pick up a cookbook for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1132,718)}早餐魔法\N作者  吉米叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1132,718)}早餐魔法\N作者  吉米叔叔
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定就是这本书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the right book?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks right to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.97,0:14:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这起司男孩挺有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a polite little hunk of cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前订了本书  暂存在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a book on hold
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,订购者姓女巫  名邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,last name Witch, first name Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Certainly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定就是这本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be this one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的书  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your book, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘戴眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot my spectacles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定就是我订购的魔法书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, you sure this is the magic book I ordered?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常确定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you say so
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(898,364)}蟹堡王               正在供应早餐
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我取到菜谱了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the cookbook, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道早餐可不会整天供应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breakfast don't last all day, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,274)}爱情魔药
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱情魔药  召唤恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love potions, summoning demons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,274)}恶魔召唤
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与亡灵共存
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the undead and you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,274)}与亡灵共存
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,274)}早餐
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悲苦一大叠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Stacks of woe"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思一定就是煎饼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must mean pancakes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书上要求的材料也太诡异了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This book sure calls for some weird ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  有没有僵尸牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, do we have any zombie teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龙息  蝾螈眼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dragon's breath, eye of newt?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰库最里面应该就有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there should be some in the back of the freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,促销可不能错过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't pass up a sale
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Found them
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须在大铁锅里面煮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be cooked in an iron cauldron
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有格调
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Classy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面应该就有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think there's one in here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're glorious
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  再来试吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, you're up again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这做得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, these are pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is served
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麦片来了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your oatmeal, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清淡又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deliciously bland
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上午起来就为了这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I woke up before noon for this?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的早间营养哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is my morning sustenance?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的华夫饼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your waffles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最可口的食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A meal most toothsome
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来付早餐钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to pay for my repast
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  我的屁股发癫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Egad, my hindquarters have gone rogue
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经不止冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am beyond offended
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁点了冻糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who ordered the parfait?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the ham and eggs is going on around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我貌似还没摸清早餐的门道  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've got the hang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this breakfast thing, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一杯牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cup of milk?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两颗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two eggs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一条面包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A loaf of bread?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有海草糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And kelp sugar?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,French toast?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hash browns?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乳蛋饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiche?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣煎蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huevos rancheros?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破烂咒语书什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this blasted spell book?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吉米叔叔早餐魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Uncle Jimmy's Breakfast Magic"?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是本菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a cookbook
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.77,0:18:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得尽快找出是谁误拿了我的咒语书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better find out who got my spell book, and fast
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过得先把乳蛋饼吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right after I finish my quiche
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能都是我煮的诡异东西害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe all the weird stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been cooking caused all of this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以怪不得还要用到大铁锅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would explain the cauldron too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有会飞的菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the flying cookbook
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜谱利用早餐美食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cookbook is using tasty breakfast treats
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,创造出了大怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to create a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我的咒语书到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is where my spell book went
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮她接单  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take her order, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  不过我早就吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I couldn't eat another bite
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来找你换书的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here to swap books with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的咒语书好像跟你的菜谱搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think my spell book got mixed up with your cookbook
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但得先把食物闹出来的惨剧解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, I better take care of this foodie fiasco
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物食物变变变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flippity floppity food
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会是枫糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not maple syrup
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我黏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sticky
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太黏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So sticky
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.12,0:20:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  手拿魔杖的海绵小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, you, the spongy kid with the wand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把法力稍微借你一用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll lend you some of my magic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.09,0:20:43.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想阻止早餐  唯有派出它的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:43.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only way to stop breakfast is with its mortal enemy--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会做晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蔬菜炖肉炖炖炖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pippity poppity pot roast
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥可不是均衡早餐的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is not part of a balanced breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个三层蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a triple-decker Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得度个假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  想当我的徒弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, do you want to be my apprentice?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可有魔法天赋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a real knack for magic
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我唯一需要的魔法就只有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the only magic I need is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the delicious taste of a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在吃有点早了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a little early for me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡华夫饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby waffle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡华夫饼是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby waffle, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又有个金点子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have another brilliant idea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不供应早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will no longer be serving breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.39,0:22:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  蟹黄堡供应早晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, the Krusty Krab will be serving "brinner"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.18,0:22:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐晚餐合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The breakfast-dinner duo
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.10,0:22:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次我亲自去取了新菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this time, I picked up the new cookbook myself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got customers
